{"tid":664322,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Google無時無刻都監視緊你既一舉一動","createTime":"2018-05-14T04:00:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T04:02:28.000Z","uid":128347,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"48c551c09641500dd5f8c8975437bf44db0f2ed1","tid":664322,"uid":128347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"最近已經有好多外國既youtuber實際測試Google係咪有進行監聽活動，唔同既測試都證實左Google<span style=\"color: red;\">即使係你無使用Chrome上網既時候都會透過軟件監控住你</span>，例如你只需要係mic講你好想買果樣野，好快就會係其他網站見到相關既廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zBnDWSvaQ1I&amp;t=440s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzBnDWSvaQ1I%26t%3D440s&d=BzsFvvO4moS6CNL1%2FM7kiIzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=37cfdc25\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zBnDWSvaQ1I&amp;t=440s</a><br />\n<br />\n以上條片就係例子，睇完真係好心寒，大公司如facebook你雖然知道佢一直有出賣緊你既資料，起碼你可以避免放太多既資料上去，但如果連chrome都無時無刻收集緊你既data&hellip;再出售比有心人&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/14/120020_923378f1f4328d9c65c08e6cba1b6e50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F14%2F120020_923378f1f4328d9c65c08e6cba1b6e50.jpg&h=7d2627f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03f2c2ce4ef530eaf1c939adb588dc487a2eac18","tid":664322,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:01:40.000Z","msg":"prove過係假架啦 咪危言聳聽啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33d704c72c12797dca9ead0060f0d3dfcc3d838f","tid":664322,"uid":86614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T04:02:28.000Z","msg":"屌， 比佢知我睇咩咸網同我老母講<br />\n今次大獲。 轉用firefox"}]}